1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:41,159 --> 00:00:41,960
Rulan.

3
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:43,719
Once you join Yanyu Embroidery House,

4
00:00:43,799 --> 00:00:46,159
you'll marry a good man for sure.

5
00:00:46,479 --> 00:00:47,479
Whether our Lin family

6
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:49,960
can hold our heads high or not

7
00:00:50,039 --> 00:00:51,399
depends on you.

8
00:00:52,200 --> 00:00:52,920
Mother.

9
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:53,920
Don't worry.

10
00:00:54,079 --> 00:00:55,399
I'll study really hard.

11
00:00:55,600 --> 00:00:57,960
I won't let you down, I promise.

12
00:00:58,679 --> 00:01:00,479
Remember, speak less,

13
00:01:00,479 --> 00:01:03,600
do more, and always be patient.

14
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:10,959
Go on.

15
00:01:17,860 --> 00:01:21,860
=Episode 5=

16
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,359
Master.

17
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,719
She's trapped with no way out.

18
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:33,959
She's as good as dead.

19
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:36,480
Make it clean.

20
00:01:37,359 --> 00:01:38,599
As for Jia Yi,

21
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:41,079
get rid of him once he's useless.

22
00:01:41,319 --> 00:01:42,079
Yes, Master.

23
00:01:50,519 --> 00:01:51,719
Here, be careful.

24
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:58,959
Are you okay?

25
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,520
Someone reported a fire.

26
00:02:08,560 --> 00:02:10,599
We suspect arson here.

27
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,919
What a coincidence, Magistrate Yu.

28
00:02:13,479 --> 00:02:14,599
I just got here too.

29
00:02:15,199 --> 00:02:17,039
I was thinking of buying a warehouse,

30
00:02:17,039 --> 00:02:18,039
so I came to check it out.

31
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:21,759
I've served in Jinxiu City for decades.

32
00:02:22,039 --> 00:02:23,479
No major crimes have ever happened here.

33
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:26,840
If this is a serious case,

34
00:02:27,159 --> 00:02:30,400
I'll never let the culprit go free.

35
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:32,879
You're absolutely right, Magistrate Yu.

36
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:37,039
Then I won't disturb your investigation.

37
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,080
Farewell.

38
00:02:44,360 --> 00:02:45,159
(Liu Xin.)

39
00:02:45,599 --> 00:02:47,319
(Hurry up, for my sake.)

40
00:02:47,360 --> 00:02:48,719
(Don't make this hard for me.)

41
00:03:02,060 --> 00:03:03,420
(Lin Rulan's Grave)

42
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:14,199
Were you waiting for me?

43
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,360
You wretch!

44
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:22,479
Lin Rulan, you have backup?

45
00:03:22,759 --> 00:03:24,080
I'm done playing with you losers!

46
00:03:29,439 --> 00:03:30,240
Mr. Liu.

47
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:33,280
Mr. Liu.

48
00:03:33,599 --> 00:03:34,199
No, no, no!

49
00:03:34,479 --> 00:03:35,960
We're all... we're all neighbors!

50
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:37,280
We know each other!

51
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,800
Please spare me, I beg you.

52
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:41,759
We live in the same city.

53
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,879
We see each other every day.

54
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,800
When you framed Rulan,

55
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:47,680
did you care about being neighbors?

56
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:50,360
It's a misunderstanding! All a mistake!

57
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,479
Wu Lian forced me to do it!

58
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:56,120
That monster took your virginity.

59
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:58,159
When you went to the County Office
to report him,

60
00:03:58,599 --> 00:04:01,759
he bribed your parents with money

61
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:04,479
to arrange this marriage.

62
00:04:04,599 --> 00:04:06,240
He wanted to silence you.

63
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:08,280
But you're so smart!

64
00:04:09,439 --> 00:04:12,560
You broke off the engagement
and ruined his plan.

65
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:15,800
Then he ordered me to spread rumors

66
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:18,120
that you seduced him.

67
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,480
But Miss Rulan,

68
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:20,600
this wasn't my idea!

69
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,920
I didn't want to hurt you!

70
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:27,360
You mean my parents agreed
to this marriage

71
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:29,240
because Wu Lian arranged it?

72
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:31,680
Yes! It had nothing to do with me!

73
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,439
That's inhuman!

74
00:04:33,439 --> 00:04:34,519
I had no choice!

75
00:04:34,759 --> 00:04:36,199
I saw you lead the mob

76
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,480
that drove her to her death.

77
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,600
And now you're trying to weasel out?

78
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:42,240
Wu Lian forced me!

79
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:43,639
If I refused,

80
00:04:43,639 --> 00:04:44,920
he would've killed me!

81
00:04:50,079 --> 00:04:51,879
I see now, Liu Xin.

82
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:55,800
You're sleeping with this slut now?

83
00:04:56,399 --> 00:04:58,360
Lin Rulan was my fiancée!

84
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,959
You and the Lin family broke it off!

85
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:00,600
I...

86
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:02,279
You spend all day whoring and drinking.

87
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:03,360
You're a disgrace.

88
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,839
And now you slander an innocent woman?

89
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,480
Are you even a man?

90
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:12,279
Stab him.

91
00:05:12,399 --> 00:05:13,319
Make it quick.

92
00:05:13,439 --> 00:05:14,240
No, no, no!

93
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,079
Ladies, please!

94
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:16,560
I'll give you anything you want!

95
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:20,079
Gold, jewels, shops, or women! Anything!

96
00:05:20,079 --> 00:05:21,240
What I want,

97
00:05:21,399 --> 00:05:22,600
can you give it to me?

98
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,639
Yes! Yes, I can!

99
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:24,680
Miss Lin.

100
00:05:24,759 --> 00:05:25,240
I mean,

101
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,199
dear Miss Lin,

102
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:27,399
what do you want?

103
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:29,680
I want your life.

104
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,439
Miss Lin, please.

105
00:05:31,639 --> 00:05:33,480
Wu Lian forced me to do everything!

106
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:38,120
I'll testify against him.

107
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,560
Just let me go, please.

108
00:05:39,879 --> 00:05:41,240
(Well, well, Jia Yi.)

109
00:05:42,160 --> 00:05:43,439
(Turncoat.)

110
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:50,920
Fine.

111
00:05:51,399 --> 00:05:52,839
Then sign and fingerprint this.

112
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:55,279
If you help me expose Wu Lian's crimes,

113
00:05:55,959 --> 00:05:57,560
I'll spare your life.

114
00:05:57,759 --> 00:05:59,920
Yes! Yes! Pen! Give me a pen!

115
00:06:07,079 --> 00:06:07,480
Let's go.

116
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:20,000
I'll let you two scum fight it out.

117
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:22,279
You can't touch me anyway...

118
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,120
Rulan.

119
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,399
Wu Xin did exactly as you predicted.

120
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:53,759
You're quite good at using others
to do your dirty work.

121
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:57,680
Now, we just need the list Wu Lian has.

122
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,319
Mr. Liu.

123
00:07:01,000 --> 00:07:02,000
Before that,

124
00:07:02,199 --> 00:07:03,319
please help me one more time.

125
00:07:03,959 --> 00:07:05,160
Help me send my parents away.

126
00:07:05,480 --> 00:07:06,959
Make sure they never come back.

127
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:10,319
Alright.

128
00:07:10,959 --> 00:07:13,240
Jinxiu City is a den of snakes now.

129
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,399
Sending them away

130
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:15,839
will let you focus on revenge.

131
00:07:16,639 --> 00:07:17,759
But once they leave,

132
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:18,959
it's a long journey.

133
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:22,399
You may never see them again.

134
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:24,480
Lin Rulan died three years ago.

135
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:26,759
We were never meant to meet again.

136
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:28,439
Once they're settled,

137
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:30,240
we'll be even.

138
00:07:31,639 --> 00:07:32,439
Okay.

139
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,519
I'll arrange it right away.

140
00:07:35,639 --> 00:07:37,519
Lin Rulan is more capable
than I thought.

141
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:40,399
She actually managed to escape.

142
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:42,519
Master.

143
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:46,639
Magistrate Yu's appearance
was very strange today.

144
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:47,399
Shut up.

145
00:07:48,560 --> 00:07:50,759
Master, I know I was wrong.

146
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:53,519
Since you know you were wrong,

147
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,560
I'll give you a chance to make amends.

148
00:07:57,279 --> 00:07:58,040
Go.

149
00:07:58,399 --> 00:08:01,800
Bring Lin Rulan's parents to the manor.

150
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:05,360
Yes, Master.

151
00:08:16,199 --> 00:08:16,800
Mr. Liu!

152
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:19,360
Rulan's parents have been taken!

153
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,560
It must be Wu Lian.

154
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:23,120
It's all my fault.

155
00:08:33,679 --> 00:08:34,480
Master.

156
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:38,000
Lin Rulan's parents are now
at the embroidery house.

157
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:42,240
We also found out the Yehu Gang
is helping her.

158
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:44,200
The Yehu Gang?

159
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:48,360
This is getting more interesting.

160
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:50,720
Go tell Wang Lu.

161
00:08:51,399 --> 00:08:53,840
The Yehu Gang has outlived
its usefulness.

162
00:08:55,080 --> 00:08:55,799
Yes, Master.

163
00:08:58,759 --> 00:08:59,919
It's been a while

164
00:09:01,879 --> 00:09:04,519
since we've been this close.

165
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:10,840
Let me help you change, Master.

166
00:09:24,180 --> 00:09:29,700
(Peerless Among Nobles)
(Mengqiu Pavilion)

167
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:39,600
Greetings, Lady Cheng'en.

168
00:09:40,679 --> 00:09:42,159
I wonder why you summoned me,

169
00:09:42,159 --> 00:09:42,960
Lady Cheng'en.

170
00:10:03,279 --> 00:10:06,159
You saw through my "haunting" act.

171
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:08,720
You could've told the Princess Consort.

172
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,720
I might as well tell you.

173
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:11,840
I had Wu Xin

174
00:10:12,679 --> 00:10:14,559
to kill Jia Yi.

175
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:17,279
I've already died once.

176
00:10:17,559 --> 00:10:19,759
I don't mind
taking more people down with me.

177
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,679
At least in hell,

178
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:24,120
I'll have some company.

179
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,960
You're ruthless, Lady Cheng'en.

180
00:10:26,320 --> 00:10:27,559
I admire that.

181
00:10:30,559 --> 00:10:32,000
But right now,

182
00:10:33,679 --> 00:10:35,799
Miss Rulan's parents

183
00:10:36,320 --> 00:10:38,000
are staying at my manor as guests.

184
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,960
I wonder if Miss Rulan

185
00:10:42,039 --> 00:10:43,600
misses them dearly?

186
00:10:44,039 --> 00:10:45,960
Did I say you could rise?

187
00:10:51,039 --> 00:10:52,200
Fine then.

188
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:56,480
Take good care of them, Master Wu.

189
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:40,280
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

190
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:43,520
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

191
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:47,480
♪The past no longer binds♪

192
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:51,680
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

193
00:11:52,120 --> 00:11:56,240
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

194
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:59,960
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

195
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:02,320
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

196
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:06,400
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

197
00:12:06,800 --> 00:12:09,000
♪For your faith that never broke♪

198
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:13,320
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

199
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:16,120
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

200
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:20,360
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

201
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:24,040
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

202
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:26,800
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

203
00:12:26,800 --> 00:12:29,400
♪One thought turns into ash♪

204
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:35,720
♪No future left to write♪

205
00:12:36,800 --> 00:12:38,600
♪If I never fall♪

206
00:12:38,640 --> 00:12:41,000
♪How could this waiting end♪

207
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,360
♪If I bear no scars♪

208
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:44,680
♪How could I challenge fate♪

209
00:12:44,680 --> 00:12:47,040
♪I knew there was no way back♪

210
00:12:47,040 --> 00:12:51,040
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

211
00:12:51,160 --> 00:12:53,280
♪For your faith that never broke♪

212
00:12:53,480 --> 00:12:57,440
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

213
00:12:58,400 --> 00:13:00,320
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

214
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:04,720
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

215
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:08,400
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

216
00:13:08,440 --> 00:13:11,000
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

217
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:13,360
♪One thought turns into ash♪

218
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:19,720
♪No future left to write♪

219
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:23,000
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

220
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:26,400
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

221
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:30,280
♪If we meet again someday♪

222
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:36,520
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
